review: Decent setup with good quality pics and navigation capabilities.  Biggest gripe, as with many apps with searches, is what happens once you scroll down to a property and select it for viewing. When finished with the search, once you back out, the search goes back to the top of the query list as opposed to keeping the spot in queue. In other words, if you scoll down to a house that is # 100 in your search query, select it to view information and then back out, you have to scroll all the way down again to continue your search. I should just be able to back out and resume my search from #100.
